# Combat Seamstress ((Combat Seamstress))
Calm and meticulous, the combat seamstress controls the flow of battle with needle, thread, and blade. Rather than overpowering foes, they bind space, allies, and enemies, shaping the fight through careful preparation and punishing missteps. Those who face a seamstress rarely fall in a single blow, instead realizing too late that every step has already been sewn into place.
-
