Level | Class DC Proficiency | Active Threads | Maximum Thread Length | Tailored Defenses Prepared
--- | :---: | :---: | :---: | :---:
1 | Trained | 3 | 30 feet | —
2–4 | Trained | 3 | 30 feet | 3
5 | Expert | 5 | 60 feet | 5
